description: Performs 10 mc runs at integer undersampling point in the grid of half-width 0.1 around predicted undersampling point, with james stein denoiser. Sparsity varies from 0.05 to 0.95 in interval of 0.05. No. of rows varies in [800, 1600] and no. of columns is 10. cov(resid) used to estimate the noise covariance at each iteration instead of resid.T * resid/n.
